def solve1():
    import re
    s1=input()
    s2=input()
    s3=input()
    s2=re.findall('[a-zA-Z]+',s2)
    str2=""
    for i in s2:
        str2+=i
    if(s3 in str2):
        print("YES")
    else:
        print("NO")

def is_substring(s, k):
  s = ''.join([ch for ch in s if ch.isalpha()])
  k = ''.join([ch for ch in k if ch.isalpha()])

  return k in s
